      "utilityType": "other",
      "description": "Choose creatures within 30 feet to make a Charisma save. Failed targets with 50 Hit Points or fewer resolve the Divine Word HP table: death at 20 or fewer, Blinded/Deafened/Stunned at 21 to 30, 10-minute Deafened at 31 to 40, and 1-minute Deafened at 41 to 50; failed Celestial, Elemental, Fey, or Fiend targets also resolve planar return and the 24-hour Wish-only return block.",
