          "effect": "On a failed save, a target with 31 to 40 Hit Points has the Blinded and Deafened conditions for 10 minutes."
        },
        {
          "name": "HP 41 To 50 Deafened",
          "effect": "On a failed save, a target with 41 to 50 Hit Points has the Deafened condition for 1 minute."
        },
        {
